{"about_the_game":"<i>The critically acclaimed mobile game comes to Steam!</i><br><br><strong>INCREDIBLE ADVENTURE</strong><br>Crowman &amp; Wolfboy are an unlikely pair of shadow creatures on a bizarre journey to escape their own nature and find the mysterious &quot;humans&quot;. Help them flee the planet of shadows and the life-devouring Darkness following their every step. Will the path to \u201chumans\u201d lead Crowman &amp; Wolfboy to happiness? Will they ever escape the persistent Darkness? Could a real life crow lift a real life wolf over pits of mutant garbage cans? ... What?!<br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY </strong><br>Crowman &amp; Wolfboy is a story driven, level based, action-platformer/runner hybrid. The characters progress through a series of increasingly difficult levels as they attempt to flee their dark past. Throughout the levels, they'll collect orbs of light to push back the ever pursuing Darkness and learn abilities to better traverse the environments. <br><br><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong><br>\u2022 Over 30 levels of challenging action!<br>\u2022 5 unique environments<br>\u2022 Revisit levels with new abilities to find hidden items<br>\u2022 Three bonus objectives per level<br>\u2022 Find hidden items, unlock ancient knowledge and save the babies!<br>\u2022 Captivating soundtrack <br>\u2022 Travel through space and time in unique play modes!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Child Support","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/339590/50ba482aa799d65e03135cbdbfe8f5d99c50dd33.jpg"},{"name":"Weekend Daddy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/339590/50ba482aa799d65e03135cbdbfe8f5d99c50dd33.jpg"},{"name":"Dark World Hero","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/339590/50ba482aa799d65e03135cbdbfe8f5d99c50dd33.jpg"},{"name":"Piercing Light","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/339590/50ba482aa799d